sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Repo
    participant Mongo

    Client->>Repo: findPageForRecipient()
    Repo->>Mongo: Query NotificationReadState
    Mongo-->>Repo: ReadState rows
    Repo->>Mongo: Query Notifications by _id
    Mongo-->>Repo: Notification docs
    Repo-->>Client: NotificationPage
